WHAT ARE WE DOING?

00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:15,828
IT WOULD BE BEST TO WORK
WITH THE TWO OF YOU.

00:13:15,828 --> 00:13:19,132
SO THANK YOU.
OH, THANK YOU SO MUCH.
WE'RE GONNA MAKE YOU RICH.
THANK YOU.

